Detailed Description

cvmx_npei_int_a_sum

NPEI_INTERRUPT_A_SUM = NPI Interrupt A Summary Register

Set when an interrupt condition occurs, write '1' to clear. When an interrupt bitin this register is set and the cooresponding bit in the NPEI_INT_A_ENB register is set, then NPEI_INT_SUM[61] will be set.
